Chelsea football club new owners Todd Boehly might have taken his time to begin his Chelsea rebuilding process but it looks like the revolution has now taken a full flight with Chelsea linked with a plethora of top players already.
Raphinha 
Just last night Todd Boehly and his team had a bid for Leeds united winger Raphinha accepted and that will signal the beginning of something nice for the London club with decision currently on going between them and Manchester city for winger Raheem Sterling.
Raheem Sterling part of Todd Boehly evolution
Those two deals could swiftly be followed by a bid for Juventus defender Mattjis De Ligt, a deal that could involve swapping Timo Werner.
Mattjis De Ligt
Todd Boehly is willing to force through that deal and again he is looking at the possibilities of taken Nathan Ake from Manchester city back to stamford bridge.
Nathan Ake
He is equally interested in securing the future of Reece James and Mason Mount by offering a new and improved contract to the England duo, Todd Boehly is showing signs that suggest he is the right man to take Chelsea to a successful next era.


